_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3091}, {\"ngram\": \"a similar result\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3153}, {\"ngram\": \"a test\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both boxed without incident in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3213, \"end\": 3218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999749193446026, \"rank\": 0.0002508691858848425, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"incident\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both have competed for years at this level.\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3248}, {\"ngram\": \"this level\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif has a similar backstory.\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3270}, {\"ngram\": \"a similar backstory\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was born and grew up as female.\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3331, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is not doping, and is not trying to assert a new gender identity.\", \"from\": 3332, \"to\": 3401, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new gender identity\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also comes from Algeria, which continues to outlaw homosexuality, which has no visible LGBTQ+ culture, support network or any progressive culture on such issues.\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3423, \"end\": 3430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re