{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3844, \"to\": 3850}, {\"ngram\": \"long overdue, full personal, legal and emotional freedom\", \"from\": 3868, \"to\": 3924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same time there are obvious problems with encouraging people who have been through a testosterone-fuelled male puberty to compete in particular sporting events against people who have not.\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 4161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 3969, \"to\": 3982}, {\"ngram\": \"obvious problems\", \"from\": 3993, \"to\": 4009}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4027, \"to\": 4033}, {\"ngram\": \"a testosterone-fuelled male puberty\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4091}, {\"ngram\": \"particular sporting events\", \"from\": 4106, \"to\": 4132}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4141, \"to\": 4147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These are hugely complex, essentially irresolvable issues.\", \"from\": 4163, \"to\": 4221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hugely complex, essentially irresolvable issues\", \"from\": 4173, \"to\": 4220}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Equal rights, health concerns, wellbeing and access to sport for young women all come into play.\", \"from\": 4222, \"to\": 4318, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Equal rights\", \"from\": 4222, \"to\": 4234}, {\"ngram\": \"health concerns\", \"from\": 4236, \"to\": 4251}, {\"ngram\": \"wellbeing\", \"from\": 4253, \"to\": 4262}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 4267, \"to\": 4273}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 4277, \"to\": 4282}, {\"ngram\": \"young women\", \"from\": 4287, \"to\": 4298}, {\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 4313, \"to\": 4317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is an impossibly difficult balance of interests, one that requires care and thought and sensitivity on all sides; that can only progress with trust and respect, by an absence of censure and blame, and above all by total clarity on the facts.\", \"from\": 4319, \"to\": 4563, \"entities\": [], \"noun_ph