from\": 4732, \"to\": 4755}, {\"ngram\": \"a pi\\u00f1ata\", \"from\": 4768, \"to\": 4776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here comes a misunderstanding of the facts, pre-cooked argument looking for its nail which is always the same nail.\", \"from\": 4788, \"to\": 4903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a misunderstanding\", \"from\": 4799, \"to\": 4817}, {\"ngram\": \"the facts\", \"from\": 4821, \"to\": 4830}, {\"ngram\": \"pre-cooked argument\", \"from\": 4832, \"to\": 4851}, {\"ngram\": \"its nail\", \"from\": 4864, \"to\": 4872}, {\"ngram\": \"the same nail\", \"from\": 4889, \"to\": 4902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up toOlympic and Paralympic briefing Our daily email briefing will help you keep up with all the goings on at the Olympics and Paralympics after newsletter promotion Why is the author of the Harry Potter series engaged in an arms-length and factually uncertain feud with the Taiwanese boxing community over the sex of an Olympic featherweight contender?\", \"from\": 4905, \"to\": 5266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5188, \"end\": 5197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwanese_people\", \"score\": 0.6152600389247597, \"rank\": 0.37317481254816304, \"text\": \"Taiwanese\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwanese_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwanese_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our daily email briefing\", \"from\": 4947, \"to\": 4971}, {\"ngram\": \"all the goings\", \"from\": 4999, \"to\": 5013}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5020, \"to\": 5032}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympics\", \"from\": 5037, \"to\": 5048}, {\"ngram\": \"newsletter promotion\", \"from\": 5055, \"to\": 5075}, {\"ngram\": \"the author\", \"from\": 5083, \"to\": 5093}, {\"ngram\": \"the Harry Potter series\", \"from\": 5097, \"to\": 5120}, {\"ngram\": \"an arms-length and factually uncertain feud\", \"from\": 5132, \"to\": 5175}, {\"ngram\": \"the sex\", \"from\": 5217, \"to\": 5224}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic featherweight contender\", \"from\": 5228, \"to\": 5262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What could Trump possibly have to offer on this subject?\", \"from\": 5267, \"to\": 5323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this subject\", \"from\": 5310, \"to\": 5322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why are two groups of people who really do have more in common than what divides them, women who are concerned about women's rights, and trans people who are concerned about trans rights, so entrenched in this battle that an unresolved issue of biology in women's boxing becomes just another nuclear button issue?\", \"from\": 5324, \"to\": 5637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two groups\", \"from\": 5332, \"to\": 5342}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5346, \"to\": 5352}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 5411, \"to\": 5416}, {\"ngram\": \"women's rights\", \"from\": 5441, \"to\": 5455}, {\"ngram\": \"trans\", \"from\": 5461, \"to\": 5466}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5467, \"to\": 5473}, {\"ngram\": \"trans rights\", \"from\": 5498, \"to\": 5510}, {\"ngram\": \"this battle\", \"from\": 5529, \"to\": 5540}, {\"ngram\": \"an unresolved issue\", \"from\": 5546, \"to\": 5565}, {\"ngram\": \"biology\", \"from\": 5569, \"to\": 5576}, {\"ngram\": \"women's boxing\", \"from\": 5580, \"to\": 5594}, {\"ngram\": \"just another nuclear button issue\", \"from\": 5603, \"to\": 5636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a visceral reaction to Khelif's bout on Thursday.\", \"from\": 5639, \"to\": 5698, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a visceral reaction\", \"from\": 5649, \"to\": 5668}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif's bout\", \"from\": 5672, \"to\": 5685}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 5689, \"to\": 5697}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are urgent unresolved questions about the safety of women in sport.\", \"from\": 5699, \"to\": 5772, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"urgent unresolved questions\", \"from\": 5709, \"to\": 5736}, {\"ngram\": \"the safety\", \"from\": 5743, \"to\": 5753}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 5757, \"to\": 5762}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 5766, \"to\": 5771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Khelif is also a person who was born a woman and has, all evidence suggests, always considered herself a woman.\", \"from\": 5773, \"to\": 5888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 5777, \"to\": 5783}, {\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 5792, \"to\": 5800}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 5814, \"to\": 5821}, {\"ngram\": \"all evidence\", \"from\": 5831, \"to\": 5843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the end the only obvious fault here lies with the IOC's malfunctioning boxing unit, which has managed this situation with a ham-fisted and weirdly aggressive sense of its own certainty.\", \"from\": 5890, \"to\": 6078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5943, \"end\": 5946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1872387464707747e-35, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 5893, \"to\": 5900}, {\"ngram\": \"the only obvious fault\", \"from\": 5901, \"to\": 5923}, {\"ngram\": \"this situation\", \"from\": 5995, \"to\": 6009}, {\"ngram\": \"a ham-fisted and weirdly aggressive sense\", \"from\": 6015, \"to\": 6056}, {\"ngram\": \"its own certainty\", \"from\": 6060, \"to\": 6077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It lies with Thomas Bach, who clearly just hoped this would all blow over.\", \"from\": 6079, \"to\": 6153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6092, \"end\": 6103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It lies with the failure to formulate a proper policy, to have a plan and a programme for the athletes.\", \"from\": 6154, \"to\": 6257, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the failure\", \"from\": 6167, \"to\": 6178}, {\"ngram\": \"a proper policy\", \"from\": 6192, \"to\": 6207}, {\"ngram\": \"a plan\", \"from\": 6217, \"to\": 6223}, {\"ngram\": \"a programme\", \"from\": 6228, \"to\": 6239}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 6244, \"to\": 6256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It lies with every talking head who has half-understood this situation, has assumed that what they are witnessing here is just another variation on previous outrages and leapt in with both feet.\", \"from\": 6258, \"to\": 6452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every talking head\", \"from\": 6271, \"to\": 6289}, {\"ngram\": \"this situation\", \"from\": 6314, \"to\": 6328}, {\"ngram\": \"just another variation\", \"from\": 6380, \"to\": 6402}, {\"ngram\": \"previous outrages\", \"from\": 6406, \"to\": 6423}, {\"ngram\": \"both feet\", \"from\": 6442, \"to\": 6451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For now, and with the competition ongoing, there are no sensible answers.\", \"from\": 6454, \"to\": 6527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 6472, \"to\": 6487}, {\"ngram\": \"no sensible answers\", \"from\": 6507, \"to\": 6526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Probably, seeing Lin and Khelif in the flesh, as people, not avatars in a war of ideologies, might help.\", \"from\": 6528, \"to\": 6632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 6545, \"to\": 6548}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 6553, \"to\": 6559}, {\"ngram\": \"the flesh\", \"from\": 6563, \"to\": 6572}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 6577, \"to\": 6583}, {\"ngram\": \"a war\", \"from\": 6600, \"to\": 6605}, {\"ngram\": \"ideologies\", \"from\": 6609, \"to\": 6619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another person who deserves our sympathy is Turdibekova, Lin's opponent in Paris, a 22-year-old Uzbek whose hero is Muhammad Ali and whose dream is to win a gold medal.\", \"from\": 6633, \"to\": 6801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6708, \"end\": 6713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999890861, \"rank\": 1.1034899846830694e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 6729, \"end\": 6734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"score\": 0.9985664482591418, \"rank\": 0.0014356059459446286, \"text\": \"Uzbek\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\"}, {\"begin\": 6749, \"end\": 6761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.519327707983851e-16, \"text\": \"Muhammad Ali\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another person\", \"from\": 6633, \"to\": 6647}, {\"ngram\": \"our sympathy\", \"from\": 6661, \"to\": 6673}, {\"ngram\": \"Turdibekova\", \"from\": 6677, \"to\": 6688}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin's opponent\", \"from\": 6690, \"to\": 6704}, {\"ngram\": \"whose hero\", \"from\": 6735, \"to\": 6745}, {\"ngram\": \"whose dream\", \"from\": 6766, \"to\": 6777}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 6788, \"to\": 6800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That will not happen here.\", \"from\": 6803, \"to\": 6829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin took the fight in a routine points decision and will move on to fight in the last 16.\", \"from\": 6830, \"to\": 6919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 6830, \"to\": 6833}, {\"ngram\": \"the fight\", \"from\": 6839, \"to\": 6848}, {\"ngram\": \"a routine points decision\", \"from\": 6852, \"to\": 6877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the end she was pursued towards the safety of the players' area by a swarming media crew, before exiting without saying a word.\", \"from\": 6920, \"to\": 7050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 6923, \"to\": 6930}, {\"ngram\": \"the safety\", \"from\": 6955, \"to\": 6965}, {\"ngram\": \"the players' area\", \"from\": 6969, \"to\": 6986}, {\"ngram\": \"a swarming media crew\", \"from\": 6990, \"to\": 7011}, {\"ngram\": \"a word\", \"from\": 7043, \"to\": 7049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her coach did stop to say a few words in Mandarin, looked largely nonplussed.\", \"from\": 7052, \"to\": 7129, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her coach\", \"from\": 7052, \"to\": 7061}, {\"ngram\": \"a few words\", \"from\": 7078, \"to\": 7089}, {\"ngram\": \"Mandarin\", \"from\": 7093, \"to\": 7101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked a question by an American journalist his only response before scooting back behind the barricades was to shrug and say \\\"Hey.\", \"from\": 7130, \"to\": 7260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7153, \"end\": 7161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999473739094, \"rank\": 5.2614014492031965e-08, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a question\", \"from\": 7136, \"to\": 7146}, {\"ngram\": \"his only response\", \"from\": 7173, \"to\": 7190}, {\"ngram\": \"the barricades\", \"from\": 7219, \"to\": 7233}, {\"ngram\": \"shrug\", \"from\": 7241, \"to\": 7246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's theOlympic Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 7261, \"to\": 7284, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theOlympic Games\", \"from\": 7266, \"to\": 7282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Which is at least, exceptionally in the current circumstances, undeniably correct.\", \"from\": 7285, \"to\": 7367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the current circumstances\", \"from\": 7321, \"to\": 7346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will continue to run.\", \"from\": 7368, \"to\": 7394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps though it can become just a little more civil, a little kinder to the people at its centre, and a little more anchored in fact.\", \"from\": 7395, \"to\": 7530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 7469, \"to\": 7479}, {\"ngram\": \"its centre\", \"from\": 7483, \"to\": 7493}, {\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 7525, \"to\": 7529}]}]}"